snippet: A 12-year-old Pittsburgh girl who got out of her father's SUV to pose for photos with a boy after her first date was struck and killed by the vehicle, police said Monday, and her father was charged with DUI....

headline.print_headline: Pa. Dad Charged After Daughter's First-Date Death
headline.main: Pa. Dad Charged After Daughter's First-Date Death

lead_paragraph: A 12-year-old Pittsburgh girl who got out of her father's SUV to pose for photos with a boy after her first date was struck and killed by the vehicle, police said Monday, and her father was charged with DUI.
